TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,6,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The expression 
\[\root $a \of {x^$a }=x^r\]

$BR
where \(x\) is a non-negative real number.
$BR 
